graph TD
    UI[Next.js UI Companion<br/>payer-policy-drift-sentinel-ui<br/>localhost:3000]
    API[Azure Container Apps<br/>FastAPI Orchestration API<br/>Port 8000]
    GRAPH[LangGraph StateGraph<br/>Data Readiness, Drift Detection,<br/>Policy Retrieval, Financial Impact,<br/>Evidence Pack, Quality Gate, Human Review]
    SNOW[Snowflake<br/>PAYER_DRIFT_SENTINEL DB<br/>RAW, MART, POLICY, AUDIT schemas]
    DBX[Azure Databricks<br/>Unity Catalog, Jobs, Notebooks,<br/>Feature Engineering, AI Search]
    AOAI[Azure OpenAI<br/>Evidence generation<br/>Model deployment by variable]
    OBS[Azure Foundation<br/>Key Vault, Container Registry,<br/>Log Analytics, Application Insights]
    TEST[Test Track<br/>Mock clients only<br/>No external cloud calls]

    UI -->|REST and SSE| API
    API -->|LangGraph workflow| GRAPH
    GRAPH -->|Snowflake SQL API or Python connector| SNOW
    GRAPH -->|Jobs API, SQL Warehouse, AI Search| DBX
    GRAPH -->|Chat completions and embeddings| AOAI
    API -->|managed identity and telemetry| OBS
    TEST -.->|pytest with mocked adapters| GRAPH

    classDef app fill:#ECF3FA,stroke:#1F74BF,color:#0F171F
    classDef data fill:#F4F9FE,stroke:#339377,color:#0F171F
    classDef ai fill:#FAF8F2,stroke:#D6A54D,color:#0F171F
    classDef guard fill:#FFF1F1,stroke:#DE3B3D,color:#0F171F

    class UI,API app
    class SNOW,DBX data
    class AOAI ai
    class OBS,TEST guard
